# Model weight files must never go through Git's text/CRLF conversion —
# that silently corrupts binary files and produces a model that loads
# without error but detects nothing correctly (a very hard bug to spot).
*.onnx binary
*.bin binary
*.pb binary
*.task binary
*.tflite binary
*.wasm binary
*-shard1 binary
*-shard2 binary
*-shard3 binary
*-shard4 binary
